{
  "title": "Giant Black Cardamom Pods Tunisian Cardamom Tagine",
  "description": "Sweet, bouncy-qq, show-off Tunisian dish featuring giant black cardamom pods with a crispy Binchotan-grill crust. Perfect for vegan-friendly dinner gatherings.",
  "cuisine": "Tunisian",
  "diet": [
